commit.title: Add subst to the end of nia in the test-suite
commit.message:
Add subst to the end of nia in the test-suite

This speeds up the file from 2m32s to

```
real    0m41.851s
user    0m41.512s
sys     0m0.376s
```

Also note the `subst` trick in the doc.
